name: BENTUK
description:
BENTUK (Shape)

Most paintings can be broken down into basic shapes.

Squares, rectangles, triangles, cones, cylinders, circles, ovals, these are the basic shapes that will aid you in drawing objects more accurately.

Just like in ordinary life, We are facing problems which is forming our current shape from the basic.

And each of us has different shape, unique.


Watercolor on coldpress paper 200gsm
Digitized
